attributes.text:
@title TokenFactory
 @dev Factory contract for deployment of new TokenProxy contracts.

devdoc.details: Factory contract for deployment of new TokenProxy contracts.

params._tokenImage: address of the token image contract that should be used for creation of new tokens.

deploy(string,string,uint8,uint256).details: Deploys a new TokenProxy contract, using saved token image contract as a template.

params._chainId: chain id of the current environment.

returns._0: address of a newly created contract.

getModuleInterfacesVersion().details: Tells the module interface version that this contract supports.

setTokenImage(address).details: Updates the address of the used token image contract. Only owner can call this method.

params._tokenImage: address of the new token image used for further deployments.

transferOwnership(address).details: Changes the owner of this contract.
